# How to Run?
# ================================================
# 0. How to show a raw file by 256x256?
# %./build/bin/raw_show path/to/raw_file
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. flip the raw file,sample1.raw, vertically and horizontally 
# and output flipped files are "I_h.raw" and "I_v.raw".
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# %./build/bin/flip path/to/sample1.raw
# %./build/bin/raw_show path/to/I_h.raw
# %./build/bin/raw_show path/to/I_v.raw
